import React from 'react'
import ReactDom from 'react-dom'
import App from './App'
import './index.css'
import {
  BrowserRouter as Router,
  Link,
  Route,
  Switch
} from "react-router-dom";

ReactDom.render(
  <BrowserRouter>
    <App />
  </BrowserRouter>,
  document.getElementById('root')
)
